Identification of my trade mark is "Happy Home Furniture"

Happy Home Furniture deals in ALL TYPE OF FURNITURE, MIRRORS, PICTURE  
FRAMES, GOODS OF WOOD, CORK, REED, CANE, WICKER, HORN, BONE, IVORY,  
WHALEBONE, SHELL, AMBER, MOTHER-OF-PEARL, MEERSCHAUM AN SUBSTITUTES FOR
ALL  
THESE MATERIALS, OR OF PLASTICS AND ALL TYPE OF FURNITURE INCLUDED IN
CLASS  
20. AND SHIP SECOND FURNITURE. in India and abroad.

The Links which i have provided will cause confusion to my fans and  
customers when the search Happy Home Furniture on Google Maps. I am saying
 
this because Google search is not limited upto a certain geography it has
a  
global search engine in itself. so when my customer will Type Happy Home
or  
Happy Home Furniture is can land on to  a page or a place which does not  
belong to us, Hence they will be misguided.

Google has become a huge identity on internet so we are concerned about  
people using Happy Home or Happy Home Furniture on Google Maps as they
will  
be misguided.

My opposition is against people using Happy Home or Happy Home Furniture
to  
sell or promote Furniture on Google.
